body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, my name is Terry Cox and I'm a customer service agent at Speedy Autos, how can I assist you today? May I have your name please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Laura. Can you please provide me with your date of birth in the format of day, month, year as three two one two one nine eight five?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my date of birth is three two one two one nine eight five.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you. One more thing, could you confirm the fourth and sixth digits of your phone number as five and seven?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Yes, the fourth and sixth digits of my phone number are five and seven.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing that information, Laura. I appreciate your cooperation. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for reaching out, Laura. If you require further assistance, feel free to contact us. Have a great day!
